ATTENTION GOLFERS: Introducing our #GEN6DriverChallenge! Tag a friend who has always doubted #PXG and let them know we are putting our money where our mouth is, with no risk to them. Tap my bio link to sign up and take the challenge at a course or PXG store location near you.
 
HOW IT WORKS:
1. Bring your current driver to the fitting. (Yes, even older generation PXG drivers)
2. Once you’re warmed up, your PXG Master Fitter will ask you to hit 5 shots with your
current driver and they will record the 3 best shots using Trackman technology.
3. Your Master Fitter will then fit you for the GEN6 Driver.
4. Once fitted and ready, you’ll take 5 swings with the custom-fit GEN6 Driver. The best 3
shots will be measured the results via Trackman.
5. Your swing speed has to be within 3 MPH and no switch hitters!
6. If our GEN6 Driver doesn’t deliver more distance or tighter dispersion than your current
driver during your PXG fitting, we’ll send you a $100 Mastercard Rewards Card.
 
Full terms and conditions available at https://www.pxg.com/en-us/landing/gen6-driver-challenge.html
